        {
            "title": "哈電發盈喜 料去年淨利按年升逾57%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">哈爾濱電氣(01133)發盈喜，預期2025年度歸屬母公司所有者淨利潤約26.5億元(人民幣．下同)，較2024年度的16.86億元提升57.18%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"哈爾濱電氣官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/01133-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"哈爾濱電氣官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/01133-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">哈爾濱電氣官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司解釋，期內盈利提升，主要是因為營業收入增加，產品盈利能力亦進一步提高。估計公司2025年度業績，大約在3月底正式公布。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15614514-%e5%93%88%e9%9b%bb%e7%99%bc%e7%9b%88%e5%96%9c-%e6%96%99%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e6%b7%a8%e5%88%a9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be57",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/01133-2024.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-27 08:32:32",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "開拓藥業主席近月斥1082元入市增持公司股份 不排除日後再增持",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">開拓藥業(09939)公布，接獲公司主席、執行董事兼行政總裁童友之的通知，對方已動用1082萬元入市增持公司股份。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"開拓藥業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/09939-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"開拓藥業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/09939-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">開拓藥業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上述增持在去年11月17日至上周五(1月23日)進行，涉及股數470萬股，相等於公司已發行股本0.9425%；每股作價介乎1.89元至2.81元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公告引述童友之表示，對公司整體發展前景及商業化轉型充滿信心，不排除在靜默期後(即3月26日後)擇機進一步增持。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15614486-%e9%96%8b%e6%8b%93%e8%97%a5%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%bb%e5%b8%ad%e8%bf%91%e6%9c%88%e6%96%a51082%e5%85%83%e5%85%a5%e5%b8%82%e5%a2%9e%e6%8c%81%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%bd-%e4%b8%8d%e6%8e%92%e9%99%a4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/09939.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-27 08:24:01",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期高水逾50點 滙控、阿里ADR均漲逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時19分升97點或0.36%，報26817點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR指數報26829點，較香港上日現貨收市高64點或0.24%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣600.7元，較上日香港收市高1.18元或0.2%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣167元，較上日香港收市高1.82元或1.1%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣96.9元，較上日香港收市低0.22元或0.23%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣116.1元，較上日香港收市高0.1元或0.08%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣35.2元，較上日香港收市低0.04元或0.11%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251126_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251126_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣132.7元，較上日香港收市高1.69元或1.29%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣83.4元，較上日香港收市高0.4元或0.48%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣424元，較上日香港收市高1元或0.24%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣68.2元，較上日香港收市高0.12元或0.18%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣7.7元，較上日香港收市高0.01元或0.16%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指期貨夜市收報26883點，升135點，較上日恒指收市26765點，高水117點。科指期貨夜市收報5741點，較上日科指收市高水15點；國指期貨夜市收報9183點，較上日國指收市高水36點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15614507-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be50%e9%bb%9e-%e6%bb%99%e6%8e%a7%e3%80%81%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8cadr%e5%9d%87%e6%bc%b2%e9%80%be1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-27 08:24:04",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "科濟藥業料去年虧損收窄最少近85% 估計經調整虧損不逾9500萬元人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">科濟藥業(02171)發公告，預期2025年度虧損大幅收窄最少近85%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司估計，2025年公司淨虧損不超過1.2億元(人民幣．下同)，較2024年度淨虧7.98億元收窄最少近85%；估計2025年經調整淨虧損不超過9500萬元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">虧損減少，主要因為澤沃基奧侖賽注射液在中國內地的商業化收益增加；澤沃基奧侖賽注射液及舒瑞基奧侖賽注射液的研發開支大幅減少，再加上外匯波動的影響。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15613356-%e7%a7%91%e6%bf%9f%e8%97%a5%e6%a5%ad%e6%96%99%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e8%99%a7%e6%90%8d%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%84%e6%9c%80%e5%b0%91%e8%bf%9185-%e4%bc%b0%e8%a8%88%e7%b6%93%e8%aa%bf%e6%95%b4%e8%99%a7%e6%90%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250725_fi_02171_1200.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 17:14:03",
            "source": "bastillepost",
